an\u00e9]]|other=from [[Free agent]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=DF|name=[[R\u0103zvan Horj]]|other=on loan from [[FC Viitorul Constan\u021ba|Viitorul Constan\u021ba]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=MF|name=[[Daniel Benzar]]|other=on loan from [[FC Steaua Bucure\u0219ti|Steaua Bucure\u0219ti]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=MF|name=[[Lucian S\u00e2nm\u0103rtean]]|other=from [[Free agent]]}}\n{{Fs end}}\n{{col-2}}\n'''Out:'''\n{{fs start|hidenote=yes}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=GK|name=[[George Gavrila\u0219]]|other=on loan to [[SC Juventus Bucure\u0219ti|Juventus Bucure\u0219ti]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=DF|name=[[Vlad Olteanu]]|other=loan return to [[FC Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti|Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=DF|name=[[Mihai Popescu (footballer)|Mihai Popescu]]|other=loan return to [[FC Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti|Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=DF|name=[[Florin Acsinte]]|other=to [[FC Boto\u0219ani|Boto\u0219ani]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=DF|name=[[Vasile Maftei]]|other=to [[AS Academia Rapid Bucure\u0219ti|Rapid Bucure\u0219ti]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=BUL|pos=DF|name=[[Venelin Filipov]]|other=to {{flagicon|BUL}} [[SFC Etar Veliko Tarnovo|Etar Veliko Tarnovo]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=MF|name=[[Vasile Nicolae]]|other=to [[ASU Politehnica Timi\u0219oara]], previously on loan at [[CS Afuma\u021bi|Afuma\u021bi]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=MF|name=[[Doru Popadiuc]]|other=to {{flagicon|KAZ}} [[FC Irtysh Pavlodar|Irtysh Pavlodar]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=MF|name=[[Sorin T\u0103b\u0103cariu]]|other=to [[FC Arge\u0219 Pite\u0219ti|Arge\u0219 Pite\u0219ti]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=MF|name=[[Marius Tudoric\u0103]]|other=to [[SSC Farul Constan\u021ba|Farul Constan\u021ba]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ROU|pos=FW|name=[[Mihai Vodu\u021b]]|other=to [[FC Viitorul Constan\u021ba|Viitorul Constan\u021ba]]}}\n{{Fs end}}\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Liga II==\n\n===Academica Clinceni===\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n'''In:'