ax|Ajax]] || [[Delfino Pescara 1936|Pescara]] || Loan<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pescaracalcio.com/accordo-pescara-ajax-arriva-robert-muric/|title=Accordo Pescara \u2013 Ajax, arriva Robert Muric|date=22 August 2016|accessdate=25 August 2016|publisher=Delfino Pescara 1936|language=Italian}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2016-08-22|format=dmy}} || {{country data FRA|flagicon/core}} {{sortname|Jean-Christophe|Bahebeck}} || {{country data FRA|flagicon/core}} ''[[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|PSG]]'' || [[Delfino Pescara 1936|Pescara]] || Loan<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pescaracalcio.com/accordo-pescara-paris-saint-germain-arriva-jean-cristophe-bahebeck/|title=Accordo Pescara \u2013 Paris Saint Germain, arriva Jean Cristophe Bahebeck|date=22 August 2016|accessdate=25 August 2016|publisher=Delfino Pescara 1936|language=Italian}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2016-08-22|format=dmy}} || {{country data SER|flagicon/core}} {{sortname|Uro\u0161|\u0110ur\u0111evi\u0107}} || [[U.S. Citt\u00e0 di Palermo|Palermo]] || {{country data SER|flagicon/core}} [[FK Partizan|Partizan]] || Free<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.en.partizan.rs/58105-partizan-sign-uros-djurdjevic/|title=Partizan sign Uros Djurdjevic|date=22 August 2016|accessdate=28 August 2016|publisher=FK Partizan|language=English}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2016-08-23|format=dmy}} || {{sortname|Aleandro|Rosi}} || ''[[Genoa C.F.C.|Genoa]]'' || [[F.C. Crotone|Crotone]] || Loan<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fccrotone.it/news/benvenuto-aleandro-rosi/|title=BENVENUTO ALEANDRO ROSI|date=23 August 2016|accessdate=25 August 2016|publisher=F.C. Crotone|language=Italian}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2016-08-23|format=dmy}} || {{sortname|Nicholas|Bensaja}} || ''[[Delfino Pescara 1936|Pescara]]'' || [[U.S. Catanzaro 1929|Catanzaro]] || Loan<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uscatanzaro1929.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=2305:bensaja-e-roselli-in-giallorosso&catid=1:notizie|title=BENSAJA E ROSELLI IN GIALLOROSSO|date=23 August 2016|accessdate=25 August 2016|pub